            <title>[CASSANDRA-7149] SimpleCondition await bug</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7149</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SimpleCondition await&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is a bug when converting other time unit to millisecond .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;now:&lt;br/&gt;
long end = System.currentTimeMillis() + unit.convert(time, TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be:&lt;br/&gt;
long end = System.currentTimeMillis() + TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS.convert(time, unit);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
